Food quality was not up to the mark.

Under the roof of Karachi's one of the older, popular and bigger five star hotel, you expect some quality.
But the overall arrangements were very poor.
We went there for Iftaar Buffet. Seating arrangement were very congested and place looks very crowded.
At last, you expect the food quality to be good but that is the worst thing about Al-Bustan. Menu contain so many common dishes like sarson ka saag, nihari and etc.  and on top of that there is no taste at all for any food item. Not worth half of money you paid there..
